Title: Package List
Text:
Spicy Meat Slices 1 portion, Loong Buns 1 portion, 10 skewers
-Bring the Food Ration Bars.
-I don't like Food Ration Bars... Can we have Helmet Flatbread?
-Sorry sweetie, mommy doesn't have time to make Helmet Flatbread.

10 Cans of Energy Drink
-Why are we bringing these... Just bring some inhibitors!
-But what if we get thirsty?
-Just tough it out. I'll buy you Salted Milk Tea once we’re in Jinzhou.

1 Set of Mahjong, 1 Tent
-Sweetie, we're not going camping.
-Dad said we're going camping though?
-Well... It’s not the usual type of camping. Do we still have grandma’s jade pendant? Let’s bring that too.
